  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Like-- and perhaps because of my unusual deprivation at birth of a father, I, I, I, I had a-- an, an inordinate tendency to, to look for affection, to look for love from others.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when you take that beyond, to give what I didn't have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in that sense, I have a chance to understand myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In terms of thinking about the war and what people thought of the war then, I have always been profoundly grateful for the Jews who put in their $5 and $10 and $20 to the Congress, who made it possible that hundreds of us kids could come and start a new life and let new roots.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and-- so that there is a tomorrow for us and an opportunity to continue to be, to continue to give-- which, per force of our natures, we must give.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anything that one doesn't give, one doesn't have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I think there is a natural tendency in us to use what we've got in, in any area, in any part of our lives.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if I've answered your question, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and I tried to go around it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
